            <h2>Books in Other Languages</h2>
              <p>If you would like to read in a different language the library can borrow books from other libraries for you. This is called a Bulk Loan.</p>
              <p><a href="http://www.sutherlandshire.nsw.gov.au/Library/Information_For/Diverse_Cultures/Community_Language_Bulk_Loans">Learn more about bulk loans</a></p>
            <h3>Specific Titles or Author</h3>
            <p>If you would like us to borrow a specific author or title in your chosen language we will need to request it via Interlibrary Loan. You can ask at your nearest Library or complete an <a href="https://webpac.sutherlandshire.nsw.gov.au/illb" title="Request a book online">online request</a>.</p>
            <h2 class="content-footer">More Information</h2>
            <p>For help getting material to read in your own language ask the staff at any <a href="http://www.sutherlandshire.nsw.gov.au/Library/Find_a_Library" title="find a library near you">Sutherland Shire Libraries</a>.</p>
